  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "A/C compressor Clutch inspection"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Clutch Inspection"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "882_5.0_jpn_11580989_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Inspect the painted surface of the armature for discoloration, scuffing, or external damage. In case of malfunction, Replace the clutch set. Rotate the rotor pulley and inspect for bearing rattling or catching. In case of malfunction, Replace the clutch set.",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000883",
          "label": "Replace the clutch set.",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. Clearance between armature and rotor pulley Check"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "882_5.0_jpn_11580990_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "The clearance between the armature (A) and the rotor pulley (B) is measured with a sickness gauge over the entire circumference while the rotor pulley is rotating. To adjust the clearance The armature is removed and shims (0.1, 0.2, 0.4, 0.5 mm) are combined. Clearance: The gap between the 0.35－0.65mm",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000883",
          "label": "The armature is removed and shims (0.1, 0.2, 0.4, 0.5 mm) are combined.",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3. Thermal protector continuity Check"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "882_5.0_jpn_11580991_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Disconnect the thermal protector from the field coil connector and check for continuity between the thermal protector terminals. If there is no continuity, Replace the thermal protector.",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000884",
          "label": "Replace the thermal protector.",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "4. Field Coil continuity Check"
    },
    {
      "type": "figure",
      "asset": "882_5.0_jpn_11580992_5.0_disp.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Apply a circuit tester to the field coil terminals and compressor body to measure resistance. If it deviates from the standard value, Replace field coils. Std. 3.85－4.15Ω（20°C）",
      "refs": [
        {
          "id": "R000883",
          "label": "Replace field coils.",
          "resolved": true
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
